WEBVTT

00:02:59.570 --> 00:03:02.774
The homes in settlements are cheap,
but not sturdy.

00:03:03.130 --> 00:03:06.931
The homes outside are sturdy,
but not cheap.

00:03:07.167 --> 00:03:10.191
(Applause)

00:03:10.598 --> 00:03:13.888
We will have to lay the foundation
of a new thought from here itself.

00:03:14.802 --> 00:03:18.549
A settlement is not a problem;
it is a solution.

00:03:19.370 --> 00:03:22.014
We just have to make it secure and sturdy.

00:03:22.810 --> 00:03:25.589
To fulfill the shortage
of 20 million homes

00:03:25.893 --> 00:03:30.265
you cannot make 20 million
25 square foot flats,